 v1.1.14 repairs the Uniswap ETH popup regression by caching approved EVM accounts per origin in the injected provider, returning repeated eth_requestAccounts/wallet_requestPermissions silently after approval, rejecting unsupported provider methods without opening Wallet, and removing long-lived hasBeenActive auto-popup permission.
 v1.1.15 restores the visible TOR toolbar/menu controls after the v1.1.20 installer could hide them when Tor was not selected; local Tor remains optional and routing stays off until user-enabled and ready.
 v1.1.16 adds user-created bookmark folders to the Bookmarks menu and favourites toolbar while preserving legacy flat bookmarks.
 Redteam hardening update: symlink-safe private paths, atomic writes, bounded bridge/import payloads, Tor button restore regression repair, and packaged bytecode cleanup.
 v1.1.19 preserves Banking Mode and restores bookmark toolbar drag/drop/right-click behavior with a compact icon Banking button.

